    ITree<T>
    public class BinarySearchTree<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
extends BinaryTree<T>
implements ITree<T>
    Class implementing the Binary Search Tree data structure and related algorithms. Contains logic for searching, adding, and removing nodes to the tree using logic dictated by the Binary Search Tree algorithms.
    Author:
    Tom Esser
